      • bubbleSort

        public static void bubbleSort(int[] arr)
        Bubble sort is a simple and well-known sorting algorithm. Compare each pair of adjacent elements from the beginning of an array and, if they are in reversed order, swap them. If at least one swap has been done, repeat step 1.
